DirectEmployers Job Content XML Feeds

In order to access the job content available on this server, you must agree to the following Terms and Conditions by checking the "I agree" check box below, as well as providing us some basic information regarding your identity and purpose for accessing the job content, and consent to use that information to contact you or review your usage of the job content. Upon submitting your agreement, you will be presented with a "authorization token" that must be appended to each request going forward, as a querystring value, like so, https://xmlfeed.directemployers.org/feeds/filename.xml?authtoken=YOURTOKEN . If you don't want this form to appear every time you view this page, append the auth token to it as well. Contact feeds@directemployers.org for assistance.











Should you want to revoke consent to the terms and conditions and have the information you submitted deleted, please contact feeds@directemployers.org with your request.
